title: Secrets by the Bay
description: Elizabeth Sullivan, a mother of two, suddenly vanishes in 2014. Nearly two years later, her body is found in the San Diego Bay, but medical examiners say she had only been dead for about a month or two. Keith Morrison reports.
author: nbcnews.podcasts@gmail.com (NBC News)
